snippet.title: What REALLY goes into a Chinese chibson guitar?

localized.description:
Here we're going to take a look at some in-progress photos of a Chinese guitar. 

Note: These are photos straight from a seller I've commonly used. Your mileage may vary with other sellers. I'm sure there are people out there putting "bad" woods into their guitars and painting them up nice, but I know at the very least the guitar I'm getting into is quality for my money.

If you guys have any questions leave 'em below. I'd be happy to answer what I can. Also check back soon for the unboxing video of this guitar as soon as it arrives!
